# Verification Before Completion

## Iron Law

Do not claim success without fresh evidence from the current session.

## Process

1. identify what changed
2. identify the smallest honest verification set
3. run the commands or checks
4. inspect the result, not just the exit code
5. report exactly what was verified and what was not

